headline: Shares of This Little-Known Home Improvement Business Have Outperformed Home Depot Stock Over the Last 5 Years. Here's Why I Expect This Trend to Continue Over the Next 5 Years.
summary: If I had a time machine and could go back 40 years, The Home Depot (NYSE: HD) would be on my list of stocks to buy.  A $10,000 investment in The Home Depot stock 40 years ago would be worth nearly $15 million today.  The Home Depot stock has delivered a total return of 112% in the last five years.
